cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI. 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to predict review ratings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to extract aspect phrase embeddings from reviews, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The paper also uses machine learning models, which can fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with cross-domain prediction, which can be related to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
